Package: MADloy
Type: Package
Title: Package to detect mosaic LOY from SNP array data
Version: 0.9.5-30
Date: 2017-05-25
Author: Marcos Lopez-Sanchez and Juan R Gonzalez
Maintainer: Juan R Gonzalez <juanr.gonzalez@isglobal.org>
Depends:
    BiocStyle,
    data.table,
    GenomicRanges,
    GeneralizedHyperbolic,
    R (>= 3.2.0),
Imports:
    BiocGenerics,
    ecolitk,
    GenomeInfoDb,
    gplots,
    IRanges,
    mixtools,
    parallel,
    plotrix,
    Rsamtools,
    TEQC,
    wordcloud
Description: This packages is a suit of functions to process SNP array data in pennCNV format (e.g. having
             snp_name, chromosome, position, LRR, BAF and genotype). There are functions to perform 
             filtering, quality control of samples and to process raw data to extract
             the LRR and BAF information of required genomic regions.
